OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fwith often clear skies at first, but
OL,7,Fcloud gradually spreading in from the
OL,8,Fwest. Strong south to southwest winds
OL,9,Fdeveloping, coastal gales in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FMostly dry, bright spells
OL,12,Fand some hazy sunshine in the east.
OL,13,FWindy and cloudy in the far northwest,
OL,14,Fperhaps some rain over Isles.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,17,Fcloudy in northwest with some rain,
OL,18,Fbright elsewhere. More generally
OL,19,Fcloudy on Monday and Tuesday with rain
OL,20,Fat times especially in west.
